| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0908 — Recovery Inhibition (sinobi)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8cf95efc-7c9d-52e2-89f9-818f19411ee8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
